snippet.title: World of Warcraft: The War Within - Official Date Announce Trailer - Xbox Games Showcase 2024
snippet.description:
Throughout the ages, mighty heroes have risen to defend Azeroth. Now, at the dawn of a new saga, the darkness calls from the very heart of the world. 
The War Within expansion launches August 26 at 3PM PDT. Begin your WoW journey today with the Welcome to Azeroth Bundle, available for a limited time: TryWarcraft.com
